snippet.title: Version 5.2 "Tapestry of Spirit and Flame" Trailer | Genshin Impact #Trailer #GenshinImpact
snippet.description:
One discovers the world by gazing at the vast sky, and uncovers the self by staring into the mirror's reflection.
Traverse the fog on the distant shore, and record everything you have come to know.

VA:
Chasca — Lauren Amante
Citlali — Skyler Davenport
Ororon — Nathan Nokes
"The Captain" Il Capitano — Chris Tergliafera
